---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Historical archive"
  description="Historical ADS-B data archive from FlyItalyADSB: heatmaps, state history, tracks. Available for researchers upon request."
>
  <div class="pt-24 pb-20 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <div class="mb-14">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">
        <a href="/en/dati" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-400 no-underline">Data</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-slate-500">Archive</span>
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-4">Historical archive</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        FlyItalyADSB maintains a continuous archive of ADS-B data collected by the network.
        The archive includes density heatmaps, state history of tracks, and the raw Mode-S data
        used for meteorological research.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6">Archive contents</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        {[
          { tag: 'Globe history', color: 'purple', title: 'Heatmaps and state history', desc: 'Daily files in compressed JSON format (.gz). Each file contains traffic density per geographic cell and last known positions of aircraft. Generated by readsb every 30 minutes, kept in rolling archive.', size: '~20 GB total · growing ~100 MB/day' },
          { tag: 'MLAT CSV', color: 'yellow', title: 'MLAT triangulation results', desc: 'CSV files with multilateration server output: timestamp, ICAO hex, lat, lon, altitude, ground speed. Includes military and Mode-S-only aircraft without ADS-B.', size: 'variable · depends on network density' },
          { tag: 'Mode-S raw', color: 'green', title: 'Raw Mode-S messages', desc: 'Mode-S BDS50/BDS60 dataset used by the weather-32 project: True Air Speed, Magnetic Heading, IAS, Mach number. Structured in PostgreSQL, exportable on request.', size: 'PostgreSQL · measurements + positions' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5" style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded font-mono font-semibold"
                    style={`background:${item.color === 'purple' ? '#8b5cf615' : item.color === 'yellow' ? '#f59e0b15' : '#10b98115'};color:${item.color === 'purple' ? '#a78bfa' : item.color === 'yellow' ? '#fbbf24' : '#34d399'};border:1px solid ${item.color === 'purple' ? '#8b5cf630' : item.color === 'yellow' ? '#f59e0b30' : '#10b98130'}`}>
                {item.tag}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-2">{item.desc}</p>
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600">{item.size}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6">Access</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border" style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#38bdf830">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-100">Access for researchers</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Historical datasets are available for university or institutional research.
            Send a request with a description of your project and institution.
          </p>
          <a href="/en/chi-siamo#contatti"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium no-underline transition-all"
             style="background:#38bdf815;color:#7dd3fc;border:1px solid #38bdf830"
             onmouseover="this.style.background='#38bdf825'"
             onmouseout="this.style.background='#38bdf815'">
            Request access →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border" style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300">License</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Distributed data is licensed <strong class="text-slate-300">CC BY-SA 4.0</strong>.
            Attribution required; derivatives under the same license.
            MLAT military data: verify applicability before public use.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="rounded-xl p-5 border" style="background:#0a1320;border-color:#1e3048">
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">How to cite</div>
      <code class="block text-xs font-mono p-3 rounded leading-relaxed" style="background:#0f1929;color:#94a3b8">
        FlyItalyADSB (flyitalyadsb.com) · ADS-B/MLAT data · License CC BY-SA 4.0<br />
        Infrastructure: Nesso Labs · nessolabs.it
      </code>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
